links.title: Moderna Announces Clinical Updates on Personalized Cancer Vaccine Program
links.description: Moderna shared interim data from the expansion cohort of its ongoing Phase 1 study of the Company's mRNA personalized cancer vaccine mRNA-4157 in combination with Merck's Keytruda®1 at The Society for Immunotherapy of Cancer's Annual Meeting.
